# .mailmap — display-name normalisation for git log / GitHub.
#
# Maps inconsistent author names to a canonical display name without
# rewriting history. Each line below uses git's full form:
#   <Proper Name> <proper@email> <Commit Name> <commit@email>
# which replaces both the name and the email when a matching commit
# (Commit Name + commit@email) is rendered. See `git help mailmap`
# for the other supported variants.

Josh Boys <aneki@eddacraft.ai> aneki <josh@eddacraft.ai>
Josh Boys <aneki@eddacraft.ai> aneki <josh@eddacraft.io>
